###############################################
# ROTAS PROTEGIDAS (requer token JWT)
###############################################

@token = SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

### Obter perfil do usuário (requer autenticação)
GET http://localhost:5179/api/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Atualizar perfil do usuário (requer autenticação)
PUT http://localhost:5179/api/user/profile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "name": "Novo Nome"
}

### Acessar perfil sem token (deve retornar 401)
GET http://localhost:5179/api/user/profile
